<glsa id="201711-07">
  <title>ImageMagick: Multiple vulnerabilities</title>
  <synopsis>Multiple vulnerabilities have been found in ImageMagick, the worst
    of which may allow remote attackers to cause a Denial of Service condition.
  </synopsis>
